{
  "texts": [
    "As a preprocessing step prior to training, neuroimaging features were z-scored within participants.",
    "Control analyses for simulation results in HCP-A.",
    "To verify our analyses were robust to analytical degrees of freedom, we repeated our analyses of the HCP-A dataset using support vector regression, an alternative node definition for functional connectivity features (using ROIs from ref.",
    "101) and feature-wise confound removal.",
    "For algorithm comparison, we trained a support vector regression with a linear kernel on neuroimaging features."
  ]
}